.Sh CAVEATS
The
.Nm
utility only requests the following attributes from the SDP server:
.Pp
.Bl -enum -offset indent -compact
.It
Service Record Handle
.It
Service Class ID List
.It
Protocol Descriptor List
.It
Bluetooth Profile Descriptor List
.El
